data.description: Come experience all the SW Florida Life style has to offer with an exclusive experience at Reflection Lakes.  Without being overpowering in size, this 4 bedroom 2 bath functional floor plan is perfect for a growing family or retirees.  Granite counter tops and new stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, new A/C (2016), separate formal dinning room, living room, newly remodeled guest bath and tile throughout. Reflection Lakes is a premiere development in SW FL with gated entrances, 2 clubhouses, 2 resort style pools, kiddipool, kids playground, exercise room, billiard room,tennis courts and a sand beach volley ball court.  Close proximity to Sanibel and Fort Myers Beaches, shopping, dinning, entertainment and  to THE BOSTON RED SOX and MINNESOTA TWINS SPRING TRAINING CAMPS!! Do Not miss out on this opportunity!!
